=== 0.0.5 - 2012-12-05
* Use stemcell version & name when present
* Store stemcell name & version at image properties
* Fix 'wait_resource'
* Fix network configuration
* Upgrade bosh_cpi to v0.5.1
* Allow CPI tasks to be cancelled
* Upgrade rspec & guard gems
* Updated CPI documentation
* Fix availability zones in create vm and create disk
* Added info messages when uploading kernel and ramdisk images
* Added support for OpenStack regions
* Use separate glance parms
* Add logger accessor
* Fix 'wait_resource' not returning symbols
* Fix 'wait_resource' when resource is not found
* Fix delete settings from registry
* Handle resources not found
* Handle server not found when rebooting
* Added basic integration tests for VM lifecycle
* Added single quotes to resource names
* Log stemcell_id and instance_type when creating a new vm
* Log time taken to create images
* Cosmetic changes for log messages at create_vm
* Add configure_network test to VM integration tests
* Comestic changes: wrap code at 80 columns
* Change how args are passed to httpclient

